Title: Dick Tracy: the animated movie
Description: Police detective Dick Tracy must identify and apprehend a serial killer known as Splitface.
Short Description: Dick Tracy must apprehend serial killer Splitface.

Title: Dick Tracy vs Cueball: the animated movie
Description: Expensive diamonds are stolen but before the thief can fence them he is strangled by ex-con Cueball, who then takes the gems and continues murdering people he believes are trying to swindle him.
Short Description: Dick Tracy must apprehend Cueball, who is out for revenge.

Title: Dick Tracy Meets Gruesome: the animated movie
Description: Dick Tracy goes up against a villain who robs banks using a nerve gas.
Short Description: Dick Tracy goes up against a villain who robs banks using a nerve gas.

Title: Flight to Mars: the animated movie
Description: Five astronauts successfully fly to Mars where they encounter seemingly friendly and advanced inhabitants who harbor covert plans to use their ship to invade Earth.
Short Description: Five astronauts successfully fly to Mars, where they encounter a rogue group.

Title: The Curse of the Aztec Mummy: the animated movie
Description: The evil Dr. Krupp finally meets his match, however, when he comes up against Popoca, the warrior mummy who guards Xochitl's tomb.
Short Description: Krupp comes up against the warrior mummy who guards Xochitl's tomb.

Title: The Man with the Golden Arm: the animated movie
Description: Frankie Machine, a card dealer and former heroin addict returns home from incarceration and struggles to find a new livelihood and avoid slipping back into addiction.
Short Description: Former heroine addict and card dealer, Frankie Machine, tries to build a new life and stay of drugs.

Title: Scarlet Street: the animated movie
Description: A man in mid-life crisis befriends a young woman, though her fiancé persuades her to con him out of the fortune they mistakenly assume he possesses.
Short Description: A man in mid-life crisis is conned by a young woman.
